{"tid":201990,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"討論香港獨立既語言","createTime":"2017-04-15T07:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T14:23:50.000Z","uid":35505,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01c138c76dc51f10eb93c40ccfc2564bf614dc8a","tid":201990,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:18:25.000Z","msg":"覺得要港獨成功既話<br />\n首先要支持港獨既本土派就同支那全部相隔<br />\n即係連中文都唔可以寫，廣東話都唔可以講<br />\n一般文書出街就要完全用英文，有乜發表，Facebook live都要用英語<br />\n<br />\n咁先可以突凸顯港獨同支那既區別<br />\n另外英文喺港人心目中始終係高級一啲既語言<br />\n用英文先可以拎到中產同得到中環價值既支持<br />\n<br />\n以而家咁只係講話用繁中同廣東話話港獨<br />\n極其量都只係本土化，做唔到進一步既獨立<br />\n就係要港豬覺得港獨係先進，進步，就要用英文先可以得到認同"},{"pid":"f1226ef0763d8ece3451cee4975290f5ff720ddf","tid":201990,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d974c36b46727449688c8f6f748320e3ba468c","tid":201990,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:52:22.000Z","msg":"咁你獨埋我果份"},{"pid":"48d3faa34b56cabfe0627611935abd0a0da40270","tid":201990,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"新加坡好似真係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f602d557d8b15c6b6f50df7f4820ee4d854e457","tid":201990,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"仲有南韓立國之後都係大修過語言"},{"pid":"adc1322f1bb164ca82881623b2bac1dbf3f59092","tid":201990,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T08:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新加坡好似真係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李光耀直頭唔識中文"},{"pid":"3a316eecb365e72e2d88be6bf8681a7830a776d6","tid":201990,"uid":106291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得要港獨成功既話<br />\n首先要支持港獨既本土派就同支那全部相隔<br />\n即係連中文都唔可以寫，廣東話都唔可以講<br />\n一般文書出街就要完全用英文，有乜發表，Facebook live都要用英語<br />\n<br />\n咁先可以突凸顯港獨同支那既區別<br />\n另外英文喺港人心目中始終係高級一啲既語言<br />\n用英文先可以拎到中產同得到中環價值既支持<br />\n<br />\n以而家咁只係講話用繁中同廣東話話港獨<br />\n極其量都只係本土化，做唔到進一步既獨立<br />\n就係要港豬覺得港獨係先進，進步，就要用英文先可以得到認同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 點解你仲用緊中文<br />\n收皮啦死港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90aedf16e5bb5cb5b416dcdcbd4f0798414e6c8b","tid":201990,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"美國獨立又唔見唔講英語唔用英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57935f85e595640bb98ba8f6a45fc3bb9f59e44","tid":201990,"uid":106291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國獨立又唔見唔講英語唔用英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美式英文 咁正個港式英文都得<br />\nAdd oil"},{"pid":"f73372e47506966e88220fa5990da76246efd10e","tid":201990,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美國獨立又唔見唔講英語唔用英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美式英文 咁正個港式英文都得<br />\nAdd oil</blockquote><br />\n咁點解唔係港式中文/粵語+港式英文？原本既雙語優勢根本唔需要捨棄"},{"pid":"1cc0a3557d889c23ee43fde574159a9dc9162505","tid":201990,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"學越南咁拼音化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695fa550b318c164f0c837ad62b781d179dab406","tid":201990,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有南韓立國之後都係大修過語言</blockquote><br />\n南韓修